dataIdInfo.idPurp: South Sudan administrative level 2 (counties and disputed Abyei region) boundary polygon

dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Redundant feature names in the AltName fields have been removed 2. Abyei Region added to Admin2 layer.
NOTE: Because the Abyei Region is included in Admin2, Admin2 will not be nested with Admin0 and 1
